This is the LustyExplorer plugin for Emacs.  You can download a released
version here:

  http://www.emacswiki.org/cgi-bin/wiki/LustyExplorer

The repository for the Vim version is here:

  http://github.com/sjbach/lusty

NOTE: GNU Emacs 23+ seems to have trouble byte-compiling this package; try
the attached Makefile if you have any issues.  Just `make`.

